    narr:narration """Anchored 2026-03-20, [April 1 is set as a forcing function](narr:Claim_April1ForcingFunction): after that date beta testing ends and public marketing, outreach, and tiered free-trial→paid push begin — advisors confirmed the date. The [above-the-line must-ship list](narr:Claim_AboveTheLine_April1) covers dev-branch merge, language pass, MVP slimming, initial modules/perspectives, GitHub abstraction, doc site, and sales assets — though the landing-page redo was later superseded by a deep-link move. Scarlet [scoped it at ~1.5 weeks](narr:Claim_WeekAndHalfWork), bulk concentrated in the following week. On 2026-03-23 the [below-the-line list was revised](narr:Claim_BelowTheLine_April1) around an [interview-driven distribution model](narr:Claim_MarketplaceInterviewDriven): marketplace browse/search, starter perspectives, and a content library all become downstream artifacts of interviews, not prerequisites. Supporting work followed: [outreach SMS/email templates](narr:Claim_OutreachTemplates) for inviting experts, and [a design collaborator's style-guide commitment](narr:Claim_DesignCollaboratorStyleGuide) unifying landing page, docs, and content site. One open decision remains: the [content-site subdomain](narr:Claim_ContentSiteSubdomain).""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_AboveTheLine_April1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_April1ForcingFunction> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_BelowTheLine_April1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_ContentSiteSubdomain> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_DesignCollaboratorStyleGuide> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_MarketplaceInterviewDriven> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_OutreachTemplates> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_WeekAndHalfWork> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "After April 1, beta testing is done." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_April1ForcingFunction> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Advisors confirmed setting April 1 as the forcing function." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_April1ForcingFunction> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "This is like a week and a half's work. Really the brunt of it is next week." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_WeekAndHalfWork> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "distribution is interview-driven, not browse-driven" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_MarketplaceInterviewDriven> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "No bait and switch." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_OutreachTemplates> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "NOT comps — a system that AI can apply." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_DesignCollaboratorStyleGuide> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Content site subdomain is undecided." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_ContentSiteSubdomain> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The landing-page redo, listed above-the-line, was later superseded by a deep-link move — a must-ship item that changed after framing." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_AboveTheLine_April1> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Below-the-line was substantially revised on 2026-03-23: marketplace browse/search, starter perspectives, and content library reframed as interview-created downstream artifacts; prior list also dropped content-site articles, 'module' naming, forking, and revenue-share infra." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_BelowTheLine_April1> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_MarketplaceInterviewDriven> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Scope risk: ~1.5 weeks of work but the bulk compressed into the single week after the session, against a fixed April 1 date." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_WeekAndHalfWork> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_April1ForcingFunction> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Unresolved decision: content-site subdomain (drafts vs perspectives vs aswritten.ai/interviews) — 'drafts' is internal framing but published version should feel like a media property." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_ContentSiteSubdomain> ] ;
